prompts.frontCover: A dynamic comic book cover for a birthday card. The scene is an exaggerated, action-packed snowboarding adventure on a mountain made of giant sushi rolls. A cartoon-style man is expertly snowboarding down a massive California roll, kicking up a spray of rice instead of snow. A cartoon-style woman is right beside him on her own snowboard, laughing as she dodges flying edamame beans and giant pieces of salmon nigiri that look like snowy moguls. In the background, a snowy mountain peak is humorously shaped like a dollop of wasabi with a vibrant pink pickled ginger sun setting behind it. The entire scene is framed with classic comic book paneling, featuring bold black outlines, halftone dot patterns for shading, and vibrant, saturated colors like electric blue, bright orange, and vivid green. Action lines and sound effect bubbles like "WHOOSH!" and "ZAP!" add to the dynamic feel. Centered in a bold, explosive comic-style speech bubble is the text in a clear, handwritten cursive script: "Happy Birthday, Jordan!"
